<function>

access:   public

name: maxLength

param: mixed, $value

param: unknown, $max

param: bool, $blank, false

return: bool

</function>

Validate that a string is no longer than a certain length.

* Parameters:

 * mixed //$value//: The value to validate.

 * unknown //$max//: 

 * bool //$blank//: Allow blank values to be valid.

* Returns bool: True if valid, false if not.

Validate that a string is no longer than a certain length.